@Situation:	break in the tape
@Comment:	can hear the television in the background the whole time; it's 26 December so you can guess what the topic of conversation is (presents); Mot prompts Chi to talk for the tape player , in a manner that would seem appropriate for a much younger child; at one point Mot says to Fat <we're supposed to keep her talking>; Mot and Fat both try to keep Sis from talking; near the end Mot and Fat quit talking when the news comes on; MT is about 20 minutes long; it's strange that with 2 Target_Children in different cohorts in the house , and considering that they return every mealtime , that this mealtime is so unnatural , with all the attempts at getting Chi to perform
